# Keep Vercel focused on the static frontend + the /api Python function.
# The Azure backend defines an `app` variable that Vercel's Python entrypoint
# detector would treat as a second candidate, breaking the build. Exclude it
# (and other non-Vercel files) so only api/latency.py is detected.
azure_api/
.github/
staticwebapp.config.json
README.md
